text: Katsuhiro Harada (原田 勝弘,Born 1970) is a japanese video game designer from Osaka known for his works on the videogame series Tekken. He was the voice of the characters Marshall Law and Yoshimitsu in some video games. Category:1970 births Category:People from Osaka Category:Japanese video game designers Category:Living people
title: Katsuhiro Harada
